  "receipt": "receipt_123",
  ...
}
ðŸ§  Notes
Amount must be in paise for Razorpay (â‚¹500 = 50000 paise).

payment_capture: 1 enables auto-capture. Use 0 if you want to capture manually later.

Youâ€™ll use order.id on the frontend to start the Razorpay Checkout.